24 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
25 Section 1. (a) There is hereby appropriated from the
26 Children First Trust Fund the sum of $36,635,222 for the
27 fiscal year ending September 30, 2027, to the entities and for
28 the purposes designated in Section 41-15B-2.2, Code of Alabama
