42 (b) (1) All tobacco revenues from the tobacco
43 settlement received by the state previously designated for the
44 Children First Trust Fund shall be deposited to the Children
45 First Trust Fund within 30 calendar days of receipt of those
46 tobacco revenues.
47 (2) The Director of Finance shall notify each agency
48 and the Department of Early Childhood Education in writing
49 prior to September 1, 2026, of the dollar amount of the
50 allocation expected to be received by the agency from the
51 Children First Trust Fund in the fiscal year ending September
52 30, 2027.
53 (3) At the beginning of each quarter of the fiscal year
54 ending September 30, 2027, the respective agency shall be
55 allocated at least one-fourth of the total amount appropriated
56 and allocated to the agency for that fiscal year when tobacco
