141 Secretary, upon the request of the service agency, may approve
142 an adjusted plan of investment. It is the intent of the
143 Legislature that funds appropriated from the Children First
144 Trust Fund be directed to meet the most immediate needs of
145 children as changing conditions may develop.
146 Section 7. Should any provision of this act be held
147 invalid, the invalidity thereof shall not affect the remaining
148 provisions of the act.
149 Section 8. This act shall become effective
150 immediately upon its passage and approval by the Governor, or
151 its otherwise becoming law.
